                " .Monitor X-section         +- 2.5",
                "  .Det.eff.at full energy",
                "     peak of gamma          +- 2.5",
                "  .Gain shift of photomultiplier +- 1",
                "  .Self-absorp.correction   +- 0.4",
                "  .Stand deviation          +- 1.5",
                "  .Sample weighing error    +- 0.1   (all in %)",
                "        Total               +- 4%.",
                ".For the rest energies,",
                " the error of relative measurement,including neutron",
