          "ANALYSIS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "From all experimental results of Y-89(n,2n)Y-88 until",
                " 1980, the authors issued a recommended curve in the",
                " neutron energy range between 12 and 28 MeV, as follows",
                "   sigma(mb) = 1.018 * (1236 + 48.99*E' - 185.0*E'**2",
                "                 + 68.73*E'**3 - 23.39*E'**4",
                "                 - 7.033*E'**5),",
                " where",
                "     E' = -12.95+10.33*log(E(n)).  E(n)=neutron energy."
              ]
            }
          ],
